    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a real rest. yeah. that's exactly it. i'm just so done with the struggle. everyone talks about \"getting through it\" or \"finding meaning,\" but there's just no meaning left. i'm just so weary of being a person. it feels like the most logical thing in the world to just... stop. to just let go of everything.",
